PEOPLE 
H. Michael Hecht, chairman and chief executive of the Broadway-Southern 
California department stores, has been given the additional title of executive 
vice president of the chain's parent company, Carter Hawley Hale Stores Inc. 
Hecht's main role will continue to be running the Broadway chain, but he also 
will work on special assignments for Carter Hawley. Hecht, 50, becomes one of 
four Carter Hawley executive vice presidents. 
